<i>A champion in Taekwondo.</i>

333
00:24:36,745 --> 00:24:38,345
<i>A musician.</i>

334
00:24:39,465 --> 00:24:40,775
<i>A comic artist.</i>

335
00:24:42,025 --> 00:24:44,755
<i>The female lead in my music video.</i>

336
00:24:45,305 --> 00:24:46,945
<i>My number one fan.</i>

337
00:24:47,025 --> 00:24:48,145
FENG

338
00:24:48,225 --> 00:24:52,005
<i>To me, she's also the prettiest girl
on campus.</i>

339
00:24:52,145 --> 00:24:53,215
<i>She's kind.</i>

340
00:24:53,745 --> 00:24:54,705
<i>Courageous.</i>

341
00:24:56,105 --> 00:24:57,784
<i>Has a strong sense of justice.</i>

342
