<i>The journey is sweet</i>

393
00:31:30,425 --> 00:31:33,505
Qingqing, no matter what happens,

394
00:31:34,025 --> 00:31:35,835
I'll never leave you.

395
00:31:41,105 --> 00:31:42,175
I love you.

396
00:32:22,305 --> 00:32:24,624
<i>This is where my story will end.</i>

397
00:32:24,625 --> 00:32:26,544
<i>It has sort of come to an end.</i>

398
00:32:26,545 --> 00:32:29,345
<i>So what do I want to tell you?</i>

399
00:32:30,065 --> 00:32:31,744
<i>I want to tell you,</i>

400
00:32:31,745 --> 00:32:34,464
<i>that by running away,
I lost my protection,</i>

401
00:32:34,465 --> 00:32:36,505
<i>I lost my loving family,</i>

402
00:32:37,145 --> 00:32:39,944
<i>I lost the look that had accompanied me
the last 18 years.</i>

403
00:32:39,945 --> 00:32:41,195
<i>I had enemies.</i>

404
00:32:41,385 --> 00:32:42,904
<i>I ran into danger.</i>

405
00:32:42,905 --> 00:32:44,215
<i>I made friends.</i>

406
00:32:44,825 --> 00:32:46,015
<i>I found love.</i>

407
00:32:47,145 --> 00:32:50,225
<i>I even found my true self.</i>

408
00:32:51,345 --> 00:32:54,304
<i>I don't know
