<i>the effect of slow motion,</i>

432
00:34:35,745 --> 00:34:36,935
<i>with a blower</i>

433
00:34:37,105 --> 00:34:39,505
<i>and background music.</i>

434
00:34:41,545 --> 00:34:42,584
-Nalan Yiyi.
-Hi.

435
00:34:42,585 --> 00:34:43,984
