453
00:35:32,825 --> 00:35:34,325
<i>As for Situ Feng,</i>

454
00:35:34,465 --> 00:35:36,984
<i>ever since he gave up going to the States,</i>

455
00:35:36,985 --> 00:35:39,265
<i>his career has plummeted.</i>

456
00:35:39,585 --> 00:35:41,464
<i>He completely depends on me now.</i>

457
00:35:41,465 --> 00:35:44,665
<i>And of course, we have our own kid.</i>

458
00:35:45,425 --> 00:35:48,185
<i>He's a family man now.</i>

459
00:35:48,505 --> 00:35:52,304
